- Berta Solomonovna! You wanted, no, you still demanded that your incomparable daughter should marry only a Jew! And here I am! What else do you want? - Fima, - the mother-in-law sat down in a chair with a sigh, - I'll explain to you now! For example, you order fish in a restaurant, hoping that they will now bring an appetizing piece of fatty salmon in Provence sauce ... - Well? The son-in-law's eyes widened. - Shaw well? And they bring you unroasted crucian carp with bulging eyes, which is also not averse to eating...